{"TopicId":178519,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"WW2 BAD-T IV BDAc AI Dogfight Tournament","CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-24T23:18:56Z","PageNum":11,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"tetryds","CreatedById":50204,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-22T21:26:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is simply awesome.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the fact that BAD-T continues to live is even more awesome!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am only sad that the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/178519-ww2-bad-t-iv-bdac-ai-dogfight-tournament/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=3459066\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u0022tank\u0022 boi\u003C/a\u003E didn\u0027t make it to the tournament.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/143878-suicidalinsanity/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022143878\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/143878-suicidalinsanity/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SuicidalInsanity\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0if you wan to make something very different next year don\u0027t hesitate in calling me!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI cannot run the battles but surely could help making rules and stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-22T21:39:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe final match of BAD-T IV, between two very capable aircraft, my short-ranged brawler, the IA-23 Caelus II, and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166583-dundun92/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022166583\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166583-dundun92/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@dundun92\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s agile twin engine long-ranged fighter, the Tallyhawk Mk.XIVb. Who will win?\u003Cbr\u003E\nBAD-T IV Round 4, Match 6:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/yRssRg5mE1g?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis wraps it up for official tournament match-ups.\u00A0 As mentioned before, if there are any aircraft pairings you\u0027d like to see that didn\u0027t happen during the tourney, put in a request, and I can run a few post-tournament exhibition matches to show stuff off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sturmhauke","CreatedById":190611,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-22T22:37:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for running the tournament, it was a lot of fun!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Noir","CreatedById":105243,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-23T02:13:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYay, I came 3rd!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about a match up between you and\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162773-aleksey444/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162773\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162773-aleksey444/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022color:#ffffff;font-size:12.6px;padding:0px 5px;\u0022\u003E@aleksey444\u003C/a\u003E, so it would be a battle between 1st and 2nd? The 2 top ti\u003Cs\u003Er\u003C/s\u003Ee(r) aircraft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-26T07:35:55Z\u0022 title=\u002212/26/2018 07:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 26, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Noir\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EI somehow quoted someone. Good job me.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-26T03:56:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe top tire aircraft would be the ones with the biggest rims, or possibly the Crossbow, since it has four wheels instead of three. But a battle between the Caelus and the Lurker would be fun to see; given the similarities in their design philosophy and ranked performance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-28T01:32:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso, incase anyone is interested, im making\u00A0 a ww2 competition of my own\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7990846343\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/180936-ksp-ww2-dogfight-competition-15x/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthis is a more realism-oriented competition, and is a continuous submission contest.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-28T03:24:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBattle of the Brawlers! Exhibition Match 1, between \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162773-aleksey444/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162773\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162773-aleksey444/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@aleksey444\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s AF-516 Benign Lurker and the IA-23 Caelus II, two very similar aircraft both built around the Falcon engine and Mk 108 cannon:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/iiM_4n-Jg4A?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-28T07:01:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, maybe tallyhawk vs snowpiercer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-31T21:45:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPost-tournament Bonus Match 2, between \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166583-dundun92/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022166583\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166583-dundun92/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@dundun92\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s Tallyhawk mk.XIVb and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105243-noir/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022105243\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105243-noir/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Noir\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s Snowpiercer Mk.XI; Once again, two similar aircraft, both twin engine fighters armed with medium range cannon. Which will prove superior, the fast and accurate 15mm armament, or the slower but more damaging 20mm?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/hkYDmkAvFik?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E-One thing I noticed is the has Tallyhawk never once used its long range ShKAS - it\u0027s clipped too deep into the ventral fuselage - which strips the Tallyhawk of the ability to try and get an enemy to break and evade at range, forcing it to weather incoming fire until within range to fire back.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-31T22:05:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223514029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178519\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221546292722\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022143878\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SuicidalInsanity\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, SuicidalInsanity said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-One thing I noticed is the has Tallyhawk never once used its long range ShKAS - it\u0027s clipped too deep into the ventral fuselage - which strips the Tallyhawk of the ability to try and get an enemy to break and evade at range, forcing it to weather incoming fire until within range to fire back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthat actually was intentional, though i probably shouldnt have done that. in my testing, the enemy didn\u0027t seem to evade the fire. plus, i wanted to keep mass down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Me1_base","CreatedById":146559,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-12T11:33:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill you consider\u00A0holding duels between each tournament season, like i can challenge the champion while not affecting the result of the season. Just to have some entertainment in such a long period.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-12T11:35:21Z\u0022 title=\u002202/12/2019 11:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 12, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Me1_base\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Arctifire","CreatedById":196437,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-12T03:43:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwill there be a mid season this year due to the coronavirus and all? really interested in the competition\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}